   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind die Worte des damaligen bayerischen Ministerpr\u00e4sidenten und heutigen Innenministers."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestern haben wir im Parlament die zunehmende importierte Judenfeindschaft in unserem Land beklagt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.840", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
